sources.title: All The Wilderness (Free Full Movie) Indie Drama, Coming Of Age | Virginia Madsen, Kodi Smit-McPhee
sources.description:
A restless teenager explores the wilderness of his city while struggling with the absence of his father.

Directed by Michael Johnson
2014
Starring Kodi Smit-McPhee (Oscar Nominee - The Power of the Dog), Virginia Madsen, Danny DeVito, Isabelle Fuhrman, Evan Ross

Featuring music by Jónsi & Alex of Sigur Rós

Premiered at SXSW, 2014

Film Festival Honors:
SXSW Film Festival Nominated, Audience Award
Motion Picture Sound Editors, USA - Won, Golden Reel Award
